animeTitle: Ancien to Mahou no Tablet: Mou Hitotsu no Hirune Hime
animeDescription: The story will center on the adventure of Ancien, a girl that keeps appearing in Kokone's dreams. The story of the dream is one that Kokone's father told her as a mysterious fairy tale when she was little. (Source: ANN)
